<section style="background-color: ;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="rte">
                            <h1 data-start="869" data-end="961"><strong data-start="872" data-end="961">Custom WordPress Websites That Rank Top on Google PageSpeed</strong></h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p data-start="869" data-end="961">At <strong data-start="966" data-end="993">LIVAN Digital Solutions</strong>, we don’t just build websites — we engineer digital experiences that <strong data-start="1063" data-end="1074">perform</strong>, <strong data-start="1076" data-end="1086">engage</strong>, and <strong data-start="1092" data-end="1100">rank</strong>. When it comes to website speed, SEO, and best practices, we let our numbers speak for themselves.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 data-start="869" data-end="961">Scoring 97+ on Google PageSpeed Insights</h2>
<p class="" data-start="1249" data-end="1506">We recently tested our own website <a class="" href="https://livandigitalsolutions.co.uk/" target="_new" rel="noopener" data-start="1284" data-end="1350">livandigitalsolutions.co.uk</a> on <a class="" href="https://pagespeed.web.dev/" target="_new" rel="noopener" data-start="1354" data-end="1408">Google PageSpeed Insights</a> — the industry benchmark for site performance — and the results were nothing short of impressive:</p>
<ul data-start="1508" data-end="1602">
<li class="" data-start="1508" data-end="1531">
<p class="" data-start="1510" data-end="1531"><strong data-start="1510" data-end="1526">Performance:</strong> 97</p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="1532" data-end="1557">
<p class="" data-start="1534" data-end="1557"><strong data-start="1534" data-end="1552">Accessibility:</strong> 94</p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="1558" data-end="1585">
<p class="" data-start="1560" data-end="1585"><strong data-start="1560" data-end="1579">Best Practices:</strong> 100</p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="1586" data-end="1602">
<p class="" data-start="1588" data-end="1602"><strong data-start="1588" data-end="1596">SEO:</strong> 100</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="963" data-end="1199"><a href="https://pagespeed.web.dev"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-460 size-full" src="https://livandigitalsolutions.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Screenshot-2025-04-09-at-18.27.34.webp" alt="Custom WordPress Websites" width="1952" height="1016" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="" data-start="1713" data-end="1806">These aren’t just vanity metrics. They reflect real-world benefits for you and your visitors:</p>
<ul data-start="1807" data-end="2024">
<li class="" data-start="1807" data-end="1854">
<p class="" data-start="1809" data-end="1854"><strong data-start="1809" data-end="1830">Faster load times</strong> = higher user retention</p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="1855" data-end="1897">
<p class="" data-start="1857" data-end="1897"><strong data-start="1857" data-end="1881">Better accessibility</strong> = broader reach</p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="1898" data-end="1962">
<p class="" data-start="1900" data-end="1962"><strong data-start="1900" data-end="1931">Adherence to best practices</strong> = secure and future-proof code</p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="1963" data-end="2024">
<p class="" data-start="1965" data-end="2024"><strong data-start="1965" data-end="1981">Top-tier SEO</strong> = higher rankings and more organic traffic</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 data-start="2026" data-end="2066">Why This Matters to Your Business</h2>
<p class="" data-start="2068" data-end="2278">In a competitive digital landscape, your website is often the first impression customers have. Slow, poorly optimized sites can cost you sales, visibility, and credibility. We help you avoid that by delivering:</p>
<ul data-start="2280" data-end="2521">
<li class="" data-start="2280" data-end="2334">
<p class="" data-start="2282" data-end="2334"><strong data-start="2282" data-end="2314">Custom WordPress development</strong> (no bloated themes)</p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="2335" data-end="2378">
<p class="" data-start="2337" data-end="2378"><strong data-start="2337" data-end="2378">Optimized front-end and back-end code</strong></p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="2379" data-end="2411">
<p class="" data-start="2381" data-end="2411"><strong data-start="2381" data-end="2411">Core Web Vitals compliance</strong></p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="2412" data-end="2448">
<p class="" data-start="2414" data-end="2448"><strong data-start="2414" data-end="2448">Mobile-first responsive design</strong></p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="2449" data-end="2521">
<p class="" data-start="2451" data-end="2521"><strong data-start="2451" data-end="2521">Fully SEO-ready structures with schema and best practices baked in</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 data-start="2523" data-end="2580"></h2>
<h2 data-start="2523" data-end="2580">How We Build Performance-Driven WordPress Websites</h2>
<p class="" data-start="2582" data-end="2638">Our process is rooted in custom development. That means:</p>
<ul data-start="2639" data-end="2871">
<li class="" data-start="2639" data-end="2661">
<p class="" data-start="2641" data-end="2661">Clean, semantic code</p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="2662" data-end="2703">
<p class="" data-start="2664" data-end="2703">Advanced caching and asset optimization</p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="2704" data-end="2728">
<p class="" data-start="2706" data-end="2728">No unnecessary plugins</p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="2729" data-end="2769">
<p class="" data-start="2731" data-end="2769">Server-side tuning and CDN integration</p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="2770" data-end="2811">
<p class="" data-start="2772" data-end="2811">Accessibility audits during development</p>
</li>
<li class="" data-start="2812" data-end="2871">
<p class="" data-start="2814" data-end="2871">Built-in SEO enhancements with ACF and custom meta fields</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 data-start="2873" data-end="2901">📈 Ready to Grow Online?</h2>
<p class="" data-start="2903" data-end="3081">Whether you need a high-converting landing page, a robust business site, or an eCommerce platform — we can help you <strong data-start="3019" data-end="3080">build a site that ranks, loads fast, and works everywhere</strong>.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center"><span style="color: #4b4b4b"><a class="button button--secondary" href="/contact/" target="">CONTACT US</a></span></p>
                    </div>
    </div>
</section>
